🔁 Flowcharts to Be Generated
Energy Labeling Validation Flow

Input: Product listing + documentation

Check for region compliance (EU, US, etc.)

Validate energy label file format

Output: Approved / Flagged for Reinstatement

3P Reinstatement Workflow

Trigger: Product flagged

Notify 3P seller

Upload valid documentation

Re-check compliance

Reinstate product if passed

End-to-End Compliance Process

From listing → validation → compliance check → escalation → reinstatement → live on catalog
